{"tid":2083942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[陰謀撚]記得注意衛生帶番支搓手液","createTime":"2020-06-29T05:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T09:47:06.000Z","uid":192517,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2a85850e4104c146a17a7d2a4e6f8bd8f785f5fa","tid":2083942,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"本人就只識陰謀論，燈唔中就最好，燈中就當打返支預防針<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家成家話支那俾國際迫到賴屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n急到強硬出動到匪安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁又有冇諗過強硬之餘仲可以出陰招呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眾所鳩知，係人都知係呃人既反對遊行集會嘅所謂官方理由係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">限聚令</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁要呢個弱智理由<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">出師有名</span></span>就係假戲真做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你諗下反抗陣營只係小小「出錯」，就已經俾藍媒國家機器無限放大，更何況係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你話隱瞞疫情過唔到醫療系統ok，但係要收埋一個未經醫療系統驗證過既病人又有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下呢單嘢<br />\n東方日報A2：越漢瞓機場百天　港府唔踢唔郁　急替六人檢疫<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200629/mobile/bkn-20200629033003280-0629_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200629%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200629033003280-0629_00822_001.html&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8Rdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=5667374d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200629/mobile/bkn-20200629033003280-0629_00822_001.html</a><br />\n匪報自己爆響口<br />\n假設！！有未檢疫既滯港旅客做過一啲「交易」，咁係咪乜都有可能發生呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在此呼籲市民喺任何時候都注意衛生，唔好鬆懈，載口罩唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，掂過啲嘢當下洗唔到手都記得要用搓手液<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"0a236fff7fe1fab13cd03588066d29461c62c88a","tid":2083942,"uid":63885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj0FfDNm.jpg&amp;h=a1fd880b&amp;s=540 \" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCDMLss.jpg&amp;h=2a905b11&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"a8ec82867a8f2638c5f2631892cf0ad2fe5057bd","tid":2083942,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f0e16fd0bcd610f423469a9c747b0d6d96ac4c","tid":2083942,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bde8de1d8265942f41fe1e445ccc2b8ac765fe4","tid":2083942,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:46:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7一維園見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzHhbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzHhbe.jpg&h=c0777e33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"